{"tid":125163,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土力量]何志光CK怒屌鳩達永遠逍遙法外，出事次次都係搵三線熱狗祭旗","createTime":"2017-02-18T08:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T05:23:39.000Z","uid":31748,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1e8645c205759c5f0b2c4801eed221df90d9c9","tid":125163,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"本土力量ep88c <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【素人又被重判黃洋達梁天琦仍逍遙】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【游雞請大狀錢從何來】<br />\n【黃毓民2004敗走時投共】<br />\n【2010五區辭職中共造黃毓民為神】<br />\n【小心票王票后】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4IFTkaKAQvw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4IFTkaKAQvw&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9cd56060\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4IFTkaKAQvw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n四眼鄭錦滿引發警察和熱血公民衝突片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AySMEXmtItw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAySMEXmtItw&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d712c1a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AySMEXmtItw</a><br />\n11秒開始，前熱狗李政西從後推撞警察，警察轉身推返佢入人群，前熱狗朱寶生趁機對警察抽水<br />\n偏偏結局係號召圍CK朋友架車既幕後黑手毓民司機JIM LAI冇事<br />\n同熱狗仍然保持緊密關係既李政西都係冇事<br />\n退出熱狗幾個月既雞扒之星朱寶生就出事（據說因為唔妥黃教搞清算，退出後被大量熱狗圍攻）<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/kq38pB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2Fkq38pB.png&h=5dbc7fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/XfcdSg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FXfcdSg.png&h=4ef39386&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/72250/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F72250%2F&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=1403ba01\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/72250/</a><br />\n<br />\n熱血癲狗圍CK朋友車前奏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9eAaYmezqw&amp;t=7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh9eAaYmezqw%26t%3D7s&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=e01bccd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9eAaYmezqw&amp;t=7s</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n本土力量ep88b 不理鬼不鬼長毛助林鄭當選便是死罪/駁大鬼韓連山老屈民主黨/讚民主黨率先提名薯片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Lv68qZKIFs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5Lv68qZKIFs&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=53214831\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Lv68qZKIFs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本土力量ep88a 蕭燈神服務西環全力燈林鄭/白票黨變陣提名鬼王胡國興/七警判得重的連鎖效應/now專益白票黨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QkZObcsDkUc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQkZObcsDkUc&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b29ac17e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QkZObcsDkUc</a>"},{"pid":"dc484f1a2502c4728fccc64fc26d12d3d974277d","tid":125163,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/bGj4Aw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FbGj4Aw.png&h=cc956c09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68300ef5336c679c6f9d06575eb8ca3a6cfa1680","tid":125163,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:02:49.000